    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_3_821-893",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "821-893",
      "markText": "总兵、副将、参将……熊廷弼本人所做的，不过是拟定攻守大战略，催粮催饷，为军事将领们补充兵员装备。闹了半天，原来所谓“名将”就是个“后勤大总管”！",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=893",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=893"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_9_5529-5573",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5529-5573",
      "markText": "熊廷弼在军事上最大的本事就是什么都不做，从不瞎指挥。这在撤还是守的问题上集中体现了出来。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5529&rangeEnd=5573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5529&rangeEnd=5573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_3_628-652",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "628-652",
      "markText": "熊廷弼传首九边，袁崇焕被凌迟处死，下场极为惨烈。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=628&rangeEnd=652",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=628&rangeEnd=652"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_7_20987-21025",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "20987-21025",
      "markText": "“达则兼济天下，穷则独善其身”，你能说荆养乔与熊廷弼人生的道路，孰对孰错呢？",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20987&rangeEnd=21025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20987&rangeEnd=21025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_10_20922-20953",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "20922-20953",
      "markText": "但王化贞对此颇有信心，一直相信林丹汗会派40万大军相助攻后金。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=20922&rangeEnd=20953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=20922&rangeEnd=20953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_6_10458-10533",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10458-10533",
      "markText": "也许是因为他太能干了，这些政绩引起了争议——人们认为熊廷弼不可能用这么点资源就做出如此多的成果。熊廷弼无奈，还得写奏疏驳斥一番：你不行还不许别人行吗？",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10458&rangeEnd=10533",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10458&rangeEnd=10533"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_5_24476-24536",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "24476-24536",
      "markText": "只是要把死马当活马医，必然需要有破釜沉舟的决绝和不惜得罪所有人的勇气，也许正是这样的态度，为熊廷弼日后的命运埋下了伏笔。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=24476&rangeEnd=24536",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=24476&rangeEnd=24536"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_10_5912-6003",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5912-6003",
      "markText": "事已至此，熊廷弼就没法再矫情了。面对天启小皇帝的低姿态，熊廷弼只能答应了差事，二度出山。在临行前，他再度致信朋友张五云交代后事，言辞中颇有悲鸣之意，仿佛预见到此番出山将要面临的命运。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5912&rangeEnd=6003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5912&rangeEnd=6003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_3_515-532",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "515-532",
      "markText": "我想知道，历史有没有另外一种可能。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=515&rangeEnd=532",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=515&rangeEnd=532"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_7_18827-18877",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "18827-18877",
      "markText": "总有人说万历不理朝政，但对于重要问题，比如军国大事，牵涉到经济或者维稳的事情，这个皇帝一点也不含糊。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=18827&rangeEnd=18877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=18827&rangeEnd=18877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_11_35384-35457",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "35384-35457",
      "markText": "造《辽东传》的冯铨日后又入清为官。冯铨降清后，官至中和殿大学士，康熙十一年（1672年）卒于老家涿州。乾隆朝将其列入《贰臣传》乙编，并追夺谥号。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=35384&rangeEnd=35457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=35384&rangeEnd=35457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_4_1224-1254",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1224-1254",
      "markText": "假如熊廷弼不死，他能否力挽狂澜，逆转大明在辽东战争中的败局？",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1224&rangeEnd=1254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1224&rangeEnd=1254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_9_12245-12325",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12245-12325",
      "markText": "但是，和过去互相推诿、彼此观望、一触即溃比较，此时的明军精锐部队至少敢战、能战，从战报与损失看，前锋两路遭受了不小的损失，但整体并没有崩溃，这是辽东军一大进步。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12245&rangeEnd=12325",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12245&rangeEnd=12325"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_4_1390-1410",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1390-1410",
      "markText": "昔日，恩宠无以复加；今日，下场如此凄惨。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1390&rangeEnd=1410",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1390&rangeEnd=1410"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_5_9176-9214",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9176-9214",
      "markText": "现在万历竟然要向朝鲜官员了解情况，岂不是说明皇帝对自家情报系统完全不信任吗？",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9176&rangeEnd=9214",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9176&rangeEnd=9214"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_5_6491-6524",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6491-6524",
      "markText": "这便是吴思所说的“崇祯死弯”，只是比崇祯要面对的困境提早了几十年。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6491&rangeEnd=6524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6491&rangeEnd=6524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_5_8494-8554",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8494-8554",
      "markText": "由此可见，高淮的加入，让辽东再度形成了“囚徒困境”：高淮与文官集团互相检举揭发，让处在仲裁者位置上的皇帝重新获得了优势。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8494&rangeEnd=8554",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8494&rangeEnd=8554"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_8_3334-3423",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3334-3423",
      "markText": "这一举动让人看到了熊廷弼的另一面——纵然是有勇有谋的儒将，也有担心害怕的时候。京城衮衮诸公都抻着脖子等着凡事有担当、有胆识的熊飞百，但谁能知道他对未来的悲观态度，已经溢于言表了。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3334&rangeEnd=3423",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3334&rangeEnd=3423"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_9_16161-16246",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "16161-16246",
      "markText": "这一份奏疏指名道姓，把所有负责为辽东提供支持的朝廷官员都得罪了。中国官场历来讲究个体面，虽谈不上任何情况下都官官相护，但最少说话要有分寸，不能轻易发诛心之言，置人于死地。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062643&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16161&rangeEnd=16246",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/92b32150813ab7ef8g013b9f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=16161&rangeEnd=16246"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062643_4_2362-2422",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2362-2422",
